  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Titeuf: Mega Compet is a French party game based on the comic book Titeuf. Up to four players select a character from a pool of ten, choose a difficulty level and compete in different mini-games such as bombe glavonique, dinausaure explosif, techerno-débile, hockey-crotte, Zik machine... More than 85 characters from the comic books appear in the game.",
